{"tid":2511092,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"縱然國安把我擒，我亦要罵習近平！","createTime":"2021-04-30T15:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T15:48:09.000Z","uid":51625,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6944a20f9d11d82e308637677467e5bd3a7208c1","tid":2511092,"uid":51625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:37:10.000Z","msg":"害得天下把疫染，生靈塗炭遍哀號。<br />\n還不認錯不悔改，把錯推往別的國。<br />\n痴心妄想奪台灣，井底之蛙圖吞天。<br />\n無能無道破江山，敗了前朝三世威。<br />\n還要瘋魔永為帝，簡直猶如智障兒。"},{"pid":"3bbd4d421a37ddacb250de4b4fbdb99163a1b307","tid":2511092,"uid":51625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:37:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58ff1ce02f94e4aead3b1bd7e5258d4900dba58e","tid":2511092,"uid":51625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d012b5dc2e19b211869d49b693796c7fa7a4da02","tid":2511092,"uid":51625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:38:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b706813833543413b94d145b6027a2b5c62c0164","tid":2511092,"uid":51625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449a09fcb10ab30c07669f0cb32066f4b739ca86","tid":2511092,"uid":51625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:43:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd8985dcd508130d4818e206245a943dd9132641","tid":2511092,"uid":51625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:43:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5349a628c0cbbfe50f40ddf4502e36fc7cafdaaa","tid":2511092,"uid":51625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T15:44: